16:46.272 --> 16:59.185 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: We return now to the
fight against the Islamic State
group in Syria.

16:59.185 --> 17:04.457 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
As we reported, Russian
President Vladimir Putin ordered
Russian military forces to
cooperate

17:04.457 --> 17:09.829 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with the French military, as
